member.name: M:GroceryAPP.Utilities.StringProcessor.StoreRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
\\[(.*)\\]:
Explanation:
○ Match '['.
○ 1st capture group.
○ Match a character other than '\n' greedily any number of times.
○ Match the string "]:".

member.name: M:GroceryAPP.Utilities.StringProcessor.ItemNameRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
^(.*?)(?=\\s*\\(\\d+|\\s*!|$)
Explanation:
○ Match if at the beginning of the string.
○ 1st capture group.
○ Match a character other than '\n' lazily any number of times.
○ Zero-width positive lookahead.
○ Match with 3 alternative expressions, atomically.
○ Match a sequence of expressions.
○ Match a whitespace character atomically any number of times.
○ Match '('.
○ Match a Unicode digit atomically at least once.
○ Match a sequence of expressions.
○ Match a whitespace character atomically any number of times.
○ Match '!'.
○ Match if at the end of the string or if before an ending newline.

member.name: M:GroceryAPP.Utilities.StringProcessor.ItemQuantityRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
(\\d+)
Explanation:
○ 1st capture group.
○ Match a Unicode digit atomically at least once.
